{"article_id":"HF7KINLI0iqNWd5e","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Hours after a Republican-led House committee released a document","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"alleging surveillance abuses by the Justice Department and FBI ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"the bureau 's director Christopher Wray sought to rally agents and analysts with a memo of his own .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"`` Talk is cheap ;","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"the work","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"you do","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"is what will endure , ''","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"FBI chief Wray wrote in an internal message Friday .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"`` We speak through our work .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"One case at a time .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"One decision at a time . ''","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Republicans release memo","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"alleging","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"FBI , DOJ improperly spied on Trump campaign aide","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"President Trump on Friday approved the release of a memo","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"prepared at the direction of House Intelligence Committee Chairman David Nunes , R-Calif. ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"over the objections of Wray and Justice Department leadership .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"In an unusual statement this week , the FBI issued a public statement","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"expressing `` grave concerns '' about the accuracy of the memo .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Late Friday , Wray urged the bureau to move on .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"`` We 're going to keep doing that work","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"because we know","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"who and what we are","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"and because we know","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"our mission comes first , ''","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"the director said .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"`` The American people come first .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"The controversial Nunes memo has been released .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"You can read it here","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Nunes memo release :","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"What you need to know about the controversial document","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"The document ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"which focused on a 2016 surveillance warrant","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"approved","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"to monitor former Trump campaign adviser Carter Page ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"assailed the bureau and Justice","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"for relying on a dossier","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"prepared by a British intelligence agent","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"whose work was funded in part by Democrats .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"`` The FBI was provided a limited opportunity","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"to review this memo the day","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"before the committee voted to release it , ''","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"the FBI said earlier this week .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"`` As expressed during our initial review ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"we have grave concerns about material omissions of fact","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"that fundamentally impact the memo ' s accuracy . ''","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"More :","depth":3},{"id":51,"text":"Analysis :","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"With Nunes memo release , Trump barrels toward showdown with Mueller","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":105,"left":0,"right":104,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":101,"right":103,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":80,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":63,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":55,"right":62,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":55,"left":54,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":54